My model's progress got totally stucked.

I must admit it was related to my lack of advanced skills in machine learning.
But these advanced tutorials are much more difficult to find and study.
If I have to ask questions, at least I have to know where the problems lies first.

While studying code from other's projects,
I sometimes found parts that I didn't understand.
I usually ignore them if the program works fine.
This should be another reason why I can't move up to the next level.

I will post some questions on BBS to ask if there are any kind of events that are related to Machine Learning.
Even though they might not be able to handle amatuers like me.

After the election on the las Saturday.
The political territory of many places were drastically changed.
Both the traditional and internet media were stirring up all kinds of sensitive issues.

However, just like what <<Trust me I'm lying>>'s author said in his book,
the media companies purpose was only to capture the attention of the public, which is scarce already, and make money out of it.

The truth is not important to them.

The political stars of the past are now the dogs in the water.
Still I doubt if these "dogs" are truely out of power and money.
They may already profitted enough during handling governmental businesses, and their "retirement plan" were already well prepared.

From the mass majority's view, only money and power are the things that matters, though they will never admit it.
Thouse who don't think in that way are usually treated as fools or beefy targets to loot.
